text: Maja Watt Adamsen (born 7 September 1978) is a road cyclist from Denmark. She represented her nation at the 2005, 2007 and 2008 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1978 births Category:Danish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
